h3. Summary
When importing a Jira Server backup to a Jira Cloud, the import fails due to upgrade task.

h3. Environment
* Jira Cloud 

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Perform a Jira site import

h3. Expected Results

Import completes successfully

h3. Actual Results

The UI shows the following error:

{quote}
The upgrade task manager has returned a non-successful result from running the upgrades. Tasks:
{quote}

